OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland seeing rain for a time
OL,6,Fthis morning, otherwise dry before
OL,7,Frain develops later this afternoon.
OL,8,FOrkney dry, perhaps with a little
OL,9,Fbrightness, although rain likely later
OL,10,Fin the afternoon. Fresh to strong
OL,11,Fsouth or southeasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,14,Fwith spells of rain. Remaining cloudy
OL,15,Fovernight with further rain, perhaps
OL,16,Feasing across Orkney later. Fresh to
OL,17,Fstrong southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
