OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with spells of
OL,6,Frain or drizzle, perhaps turning more
OL,7,Fpersistent for a time in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Less windy.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FBrighter on Thursday with showers
OL,12,Flikely later. Bright with showers on
OL,13,FFriday, windy later. Drier on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
